62
00:05:16.566 --> 00:05:19.444
The question is. do you win?

63
00:05:35.752 --> 00:05:38.504
Cuz. so how was your blind date?

64
00:05:45.053 --> 00:05:47.764
You know. cuz? Total waste of time.

65
00:05:53.019 --> 00:05:54.020
and he has a kid.

66
